dct_title_s: The Rand-McNally new library atlas map of India
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures.; Insets: Extension of Malay Peninsula -- Southeastern provinces of India (further India) -- Nicobar Islands.; Shows "British Provinces," "Feudatory States" and "Independent States and Colonies."; Page 83 and 84 of "Library Atlas of the World."
